# Scenic Doors Pricing App — Core

## Stack & Scripts

- **Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind**, Firebase optional
- Scripts: `pnpm dev`, `pnpm build`, `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck`

## Providers

- `src/app/providers.tsx` **must** mount `QuoteProvider`

## Lint/Type Hygiene

- No `any`; prefix intentionally unused variables/params with `_`
- Correct hook deps; fix stale state
- Prefer Next `<Image />` for local assets; for legit external/dynamic `<img>`, add a **targeted** `/* eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element */` only above that line

## Acceptance (each step)

- Dev/build run clean
- Provide explicit URLs/log lines/tests for verification

## Notes

- Dashboard charts populate only when `quotes` collection has data; seed 2–3 quotes if empty
